{"tid":911381,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳凱欣偕王祖藍聽初創青年分享　維港見「請支持」霓虹燈飾","createTime":"2018-11-22T01:23:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-23T04:32:09.000Z","uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3bb8261a218eb3fe6b15ff7b535c8cd76183275d","tid":911381,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T01:23:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181121/s00001/211da7c3be2fdb72a7d01dc6c61f2fe2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181121%2Fs00001%2F211da7c3be2fdb72a7d01dc6c61f2fe2.jpg&h=55f15a3e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181121/s00001/213f2afdea9dfc3e57ee37b2b3dd8f5d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181121%2Fs00001%2F213f2afdea9dfc3e57ee37b2b3dd8f5d.jpg&h=895c4d22&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181121/s00001/227bb586c8d2322b513e7664f999190e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181121%2Fs00001%2F227bb586c8d2322b513e7664f999190e.jpg&h=7188509f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n <br />\n立法會九龍西補選星期日（25日）就舉行，陳凱欣今日就同埋藝人兼廣西政協王祖藍，一齊去聽科創同初創青年分享，同場仲有民建聯嘅九龍西立法會議員鄭泳舜。<br />\n<br />\n陳凱欣係facebook話，「忙碌的選舉期仍同祖藍一齊去聆聽科創、初創青年的簡介及心聲」，仲話任何時候都有新的挑戰，同時亦有新機遇，「只要用心、用人，便可成就一番事業」。<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，雖則陳凱欣多次話自己選情嚴峻，不過睇嚟佢背後仍然有好多雄厚力量支持。今晚網傳，喺維港璀璨嘅燈飾之中，由港島眺望紅磡祥祺中心方向，可以見到「請支持陳凱欣」嘅巨型霓虹燈飾，令Emily憶起當日仍然身為「健康大使」嘅陳凱欣，喺紅磡多間殯儀館後嗰幅巨型海報。唔知道今次喺有人別有用心，定係不謀而合呢？<br />\n<br />\n除此之外，九龍一份地區報《龍週》，亦用陳凱欣選情嚴峻為今日頭版，內文仲話遭到對手團隊抹黑滋擾，又叫大家全家總動員一票都不能少。翻查資料，呢份《龍週》背後4名董事等負責人，有至少兩個係同鄉會同工商總會之類啲建制背景。睇嚟陳凱欣嘅支持者，喺選舉最後階段，都默默地用唔同嘅手法為佢加持。<br />\n<br />\n補充番，今次補選其他候選人有伍廸希、曾麗文、李卓人同馮檢基。<br />\n<br />\nEmily Online<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181121/s00001/1542806857839?web_push=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181121%2Fs00001%2F1542806857839%3Fweb_push%3D1&d=6Zvx9h4%2B8YMvnTGnfB%2FsIf1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=339ad285\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181121%2Fs00001%2F1542806857839%3Fweb_push%3D1&h=b6ca2425\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181121/s00001/1542806857839?web_push=1</a>"},{"pid":"ee023d8db766864b10e76ff76daa00a513352a38","tid":911381,"uid":115189,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T01:25:09.000Z","msg":"王祖紅，係咁㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"449664dd0233d50a6a94a45dc0c7a410845e0ab6","tid":911381,"uid":61271,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T01:38:35.000Z","msg":"仆街啦奶共狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n生仔無屎忽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e922bb37d9f0a4119a4cbbe793a2484648c2ba8","tid":911381,"uid":44358,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T01:44:52.000Z","msg":"好多連登仔同王蛆藍一樣，唔想隻臭閪輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b63c6907306a96677b4c0c3108119505adaf108e","tid":911381,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"449664dd0233d50a6a94a45dc0c7a410845e0ab6","tid":911381,"uid":61271,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T01:38:35.000Z","msg":"仆街啦奶共狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n生仔無屎忽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T02:21:42.000Z","msg":"老子認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed7bb72f0129904d40da4c556de1d01078c7d2a8","tid":911381,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB